title: Rick and Morty Can Solve Your Procrastination Problem

media:group.media:title: Rick and Morty Can Solve Your Procrastination Problem
media:group.media:description:
Procrastination plagues us all, including fictional characters Rick and Morty. In Season 6, Episode 4, Rick Sanchez invents a “Somnambulator” to get work done while he’s sleeping. Humans, unfortunately, can’t rely on sci-fi technology to save us. What can help us, however, is learning how to sympathize with our future selves.
